column5: Last year I hunted hard all season to get a small jake in the closing week. This year I lucked out and got a tom on my first hunt. 17.3lbs  8 1/2" beard and 7/8 spurs. Picked up my 2nd tag today and ready to get back at it
Nice bird, where's the taters and gravy..
Congrats! What did you do differently this year?  S.
Congrats! What did you do differently this year?  S. The property I hunt has a few different guys hunting it and there hasnt been alot of birds around the last few years. I struck first this year !
Nice job Rich.  At first I thought you had got that bird up where I met you in the fall. I was half-way out the door for a tag.

Nice job Rich.  At first I thought you had got that bird up where I met you in the fall. I was half-way out the door for a tag. haha  nope .. but it wouldnt be a bad spot to be. I will probobly give it a try myself.
sweet! hope i get one soon...
